claim: The Communist Party of Cuba's First Secretary is Fidel Castro's younger brother.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Since April 2011 , the First Secretary of the Communist Party of Cuba has been Raúl Castro , the President of Cuba , younger brother of the previous First Secretary and President of Cuba , Fidel Castro who died on 25 November 2016 , and the Second Secretary has been José Ramón Machado Ventura .
